<h2><span><span class="conr">#2</span> <a href="viewtopic.php?pid=1197#p1197">2017-05-08 19:53:37</a></span></h2>
<div class="box">
<div class="inbox">
<div class="postbody">
<div class="postleft">
<dl>
<dt><strong><a href="profile.php?id=3856">gnugr</a></strong></dt>
<dd class="usertitle"><strong>Community Member</strong></dd>
<dd><span>Registered: 2017-02-28</span></dd>
<dd><span>Posts: 31</span></dd>
</dl>
</div>
<div class="postright">
<h3>Re: USB Encrypted Persistence</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>Try &quot;echo &quot;union&quot; &gt; /mnt/my_usb/persistence.conf&quot; or &quot;echo $union &gt;&gt; /mnt/my_usb/persistence.conf&quot;, sure with &#039;sudo&#039; if the $PATH is for super user.</p>
</div>
